[
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"psasuper\">For the <st data-num=\"05329\" class=\"\">music director</st>, a <st data-num=\"04210\" class=\"\">psalm</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\">David</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">How <st data-num=\"0835\" class=\"\">blessed</st><n id=\"1\" /> is the one who <st data-num=\"07919 0413\">treats</st> the <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">poor</st> <st data-num=\"07919 0413\">properly</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">When</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">trouble</st> comes,<n id=\"3\" /> may<n id=\"4\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">deliver</st> him.<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">May the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">protect</st> him and <st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">save</st> his <st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">life</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">May he be <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">blessed</st><n id=\"2\" /> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">turn</st> him <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">over</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05582\" class=\"\">supports</st><n id=\"1\" /> him <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> his <st data-num=\"06210 01741\">sickbed</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you have <st data-num=\"02015\" class=\"\">healed</st> <st data-num=\"03605 04904\">him</st> from his <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">illness</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">As for <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">me</st>, I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cO <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"02603\" class=\"\">have mercy on</st> me!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07495\" class=\"\">Heal</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">me</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> I have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st> against you.</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">ask</st> this <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">cruel question</st> about me,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"04970\" class=\"\">When</st> will he finally <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">die</st> and be <st data-num=\"06 08034\">forgotten</st>?\u2019<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">When</st> someone <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">comes</st> to <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">visit</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> he <st data-num=\"07723 01696\">pretends to be friendly</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">thinks of</st> <st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">ways to defame</st> me,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and when he <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">leaves</st> he <st data-num=\"02351 01696\">slanders</st> me.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> who <st data-num=\"08130\" class=\"\">hate</st> me <st data-num=\"03907\" class=\"\">whisper</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">insults about</st> me <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">to one another</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">plan</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">ways to harm</st> me.</p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They say,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018An <st data-num=\"01100\" class=\"\">awful</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">disease</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03332\" class=\"\">overwhelms</st> him,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">now that</st> he is <st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">bedridden</st> he will <st data-num=\"03808 03254\">never</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">recover</st>.\u2019<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">Even</st> my <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">close</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">friend</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> I <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trusted</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">he who <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">shared</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">meals</st> with me, has <st data-num=\"01431 06119\">turned</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> me.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">As for <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, O <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"02603\" class=\"\">have mercy on</st> me and <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">raise</st> me <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">up</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">so I can <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">pay</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">them</st> <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">back</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">By <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st><n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> you are <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">pleased</st> with me,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> my <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st> does<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07321\" class=\"\">triumph</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> me.</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">As for <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">me</st>, you <st data-num=\"08551\" class=\"\">uphold</st><n id=\"1\" /> me because of my <st data-num=\"08537\" class=\"\">integrity</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"05324\">allow</st><n id=\"3\" /> me <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">permanent</st> <st data-num=\"05324\" class=\"\">access</st> to your <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Psalms",
    "chapter": "41",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">deserves praise</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">future</st> and <st data-num=\"05704 05769\">forevermore</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">We <st data-num=\"0543\" class=\"\">agree</st>! We <st data-num=\"0543\" class=\"\">agree</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  }
]